{"tid":841160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果今日係你人生既最後一日，你會寫封點樣既遺書","createTime":"2018-09-29T11:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T12:45:56.000Z","uid":208035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"794987992bfb9ee2fcacc7c419d5a421542a3ca2","tid":841160,"uid":208035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T11:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dc06e65792542bc07073495e70c01156a71389","tid":841160,"uid":1249,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T11:28:13.000Z","msg":"唔撚寫"},{"pid":"caff74b4c6dcb224c2b86356397dd8b76d870b46","tid":841160,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"阿欣我真係好鐘意你<br />\n係我今生結束前 我好想同你講你真係好靚<br />\n雖然你唔知我係邊個 但係我已經留意咗你好耐<br />\n每次你黎我間餐廳我都好開心<br />\n你係我留係呢間垃圾公司既原動力<br />\n所以呢封遺書我想你原諒我私下查過你叫咩名<br />\n仲有查過你屋企同學校<br />\n仲有攞過你門口啲垃圾<br />\n仲有私自幫你趕走騷擾你既籃球隊學長<br />\n仲有係你對面屋租咗間房偷望你<br />\n仲有問你朋友阿儀買你既相貼滿全屋<br />\n雖然係我去美國做神父之前既事<br />\n但我真係唔係變態佬好希望你原諒我"},{"pid":"05e909ffb27325cdcf18ad2cdfc106a9a923f487","tid":841160,"uid":133252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"出現係依個世界真係對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4f00fabf1c6a65cf92afd25e9a903c505501d4","tid":841160,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T11:52:39.000Z","msg":"都冇人想睇"},{"pid":"8ec507af933d88324c27d0019493179389d204e0","tid":841160,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T11:57:39.000Z","msg":"你地慢慢挨 我走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5eb8692d4c5bb13cd41886c1653788af368e234","tid":841160,"uid":18226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:00: